name: Gimme A Lift!
Lore: 'Jar Jar Binks''s courage on the battlefield put quite a thorn in the Trade Federation''s side. Many believed it wasn''t actually courage.',
Text: 'Relocate Jar Jar to a battle just initiated at an adjacent site. OR Increase Jar Jar''s landspeed by 1 for remainder of turn. OR If Jar Jar on Brisky Morning Munchen, take him into hand.',
